msgid "You can now drink with Ando-san and Kaneko-san!\n\nAs you become closer to the customers, your rank within\nthe bar will increase. As your rank increases, you'll\nbe able to drink with more people.\n\nBe assertive about approaching people, or form a bond\nthrough karaoke or darts.\n\nIt'd be great if everyone got along.\nI'm sure Mama would be happy..."
